'''帕魯布·科里''' （Purab Kohli）是印度的電視和電影演員，模特兒和前[[影像騎師|影像騎師]]。

==個人生活==
Kohli的父親Harsh是一家旅館經營者和電影製片人，他的母親是企業培訓師。 他在孟買郊外的班德拉（Bandra）的聖斯坦尼斯勞斯中學（St. Stanislaus High School）和馬哈拉施特拉邦浦那的主教學校（Bishop's School）上學。 他將其教育係從科學系轉為商業系，最後轉為藝術系，並研究了經濟學，心理學和文學。 他加入了一所飛行學校當飛行員，但沒有繼續。

Kohli於2018年2月15日在果阿舉行的私人儀式上與他的老友Lucy Payton結婚。這對夫婦有一個女兒Inaya（生於2015年）<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Sunder |first=Shubangi |title='Be inspired and make a difference' |url=http://thestudentsmag.com/story_content?article=%20'Be%20inspired%20and%20make%20a%20difference' |date=2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012013217/http://thestudentsmag.com/story_content?article=%20%27Be%20inspired%20and%20make%20a%20difference%27 |archive-date=12 October 2013 |magazine=The Students |accessdate=27 February 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Purab Kohli and Lucy Paton take wedding vows in Goa |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/purab-kohli-lucy-paton-wedding-see-photos-5067509/ |date=17 February 2018 |newspaper=The Indian Express |access-date=2 July 2019 |archive-date=2019-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321173007/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/purab-kohli-lucy-paton-wedding-see-photos-5067509/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

前演員比沙姆·科利（Bhisham Kohli）也就是維沙爾·阿南德（Vishal Anand）是他的父親叔叔（父親的兄弟）。 Kohli的祖母是Dev Anand的姐姐（因此讓Kohli成為了已故演員的外））。 因此，電影製片人謝卡·卡普爾（Shekhar Kapur）（是Dev Anand的另一個姐妹的兒子）是Kohli的叔叔<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://in.askmen.com/celeb-interviews/1101156/article/celeb-speak-actor-purab-kohli-on-career-his-love-for-dance-a |title=Celeb Speak: Actor Purab Kohli On Career, His Love For Dance And Upcoming Projects |access-date=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709185017/http://in.askmen.com/celeb-interviews/1101156/article/celeb-speak-actor-purab-kohli-on-career-his-love-for-dance-a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。


==職業生涯==
Kohli的職業生涯始於Zee電視台的電視節目Hip Hip Hurray的演員，並通過第五頻道的視頻騎師獲得了認可。隨後，他主持了旅行節目Gone India，並在印度進行了預算旅行<ref name=Tribune>{{cite news |url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2000/20000227/spectrum/tv.htm |title=Purab goes paschim and dakshin |newspaper=[[The_Tribune_(Chandigarh)|The Tribune]] |date=27 February 2000 |accessdate=20 November 2012 |archive-date=2017-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628045816/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2000/20000227/spectrum/tv.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Kohli在Rock On的作品在2009年3月的2009電影大獎上獲得了特別評審團獎。<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/Filmfare+certificate+was+a+pleasant+surprise:+Purab+Kohli/1/33483.html |location=New Delhi |date=23 March 2009 |title=Filmfare certificate was a pleasant surprise: Purab Kohli |accessdate=20 November 2012 |magazine=[[India_Today|India Today]] |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105953/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/Filmfare+certificate+was+a+pleasant+surprise:+Purab+Kohli/1/33483.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 



